254
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:39,520
I will do my best.

255
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,040
We're off.

256
00:11:42,530 --> 00:11:43,370
Come on.

257
00:11:58,560 --> 00:12:00,410
What specific exercises need to be done?

258
00:12:01,170 --> 00:12:02,080
At this stage,

259
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:03,410
