260
00:12:03,410 --> 00:12:04,960
back to a level

261
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:05,920
for daily activities.

262
00:12:06,130 --> 00:12:07,890
What should we pay attention to?

263
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,320
At the early stage of rehabilitation,

264
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:11,010
