265
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:12,250
Especially the injured area.

266
00:12:12,370 --> 00:12:14,560
He should avoid large bending movements.

267
00:12:15,290 --> 00:12:16,370
Is there any way

268
00:12:16,370 --> 00:12:17,530
to recover a bit faster?

269
00:12:18,010 --> 00:12:19,530
Rehabilitation training can't be rushed.

270
00:12:19,530 --> 00:12:20,650
It needs to be done step by step.

271
00:12:20,650 --> 00:12:22,680
If you want to help him recover faster,

272
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:24,250
you can conduct rehabilitation training

273
00:12:24,250 --> 00:12:25,840
for uninjured areas

274
00:12:25,890 --> 00:12:27,080
to prevent muscle wasting.

275
00:12:27,490 --> 00:12:28,330
Secondly,

276
00:12:28,410 --> 00:12:31,050
conduct appropriate cardio training

277
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:33,010
to maintain good physical function.

278
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:39,170
Chi, time to eat.

279
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,530
I brought you some bone broth

280
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:41,680
