282
00:12:46,680 --> 00:12:48,170
This was not bought outside.

283
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,530
I brewed it at home.

284
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:51,600
I also selected the bones personally.

285
00:12:52,170 --> 00:12:53,490
I knew you need to eat light food

286
00:12:53,490 --> 00:12:54,330
after the surgery,

287
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:55,720
so I only added a bit of salt

288
00:12:55,720 --> 00:12:56,920
and didn't put anything else in it.

289
00:12:58,010 --> 00:12:59,050
Not because of this.

290
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,410
Your mom simmered soup all afternoon

291
00:13:02,530 --> 00:13:03,890
to nourish you.

292
00:13:04,250 --> 00:13:05,650
Can't you even take a sip?

293
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:11,050
Dad, Mom,

294
00:13:11,680 --> 00:13:12,890
you may not know

295
00:13:13,170 --> 00:13:15,410
that one positive drug test

296
00:13:15,530 --> 00:13:17,560
may affect the entire career of an athlete.

297
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,920
So athletes must be very cautious

298
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:21,440
about the food they eat.

299
00:13:22,650 --> 00:13:23,650
Because of this,

300
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:25,080
I haven't eaten the meat

301
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,170
outside for many years.

302
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,320
I haven't taken good care

303
00:13:30,680 --> 00:13:32,440
of you all these years.

304
00:13:33,370 --> 00:13:34,600
I didn't even know these things.

305
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:36,050
It's not that.

306
00:13:37,770 --> 00:13:39,890
I should apologize to you.

307
00:13:40,560 --> 00:13:42,490
I've made you anxious these days.

308
00:13:51,920 --> 00:13:54,130
Actually, I deceived you when I promised

309
00:13:54,410 --> 00:13:55,650
that I wouldn't get hurt.

310
00:13:56,170 --> 00:13:57,170
As an athlete,

311
00:13:57,680 --> 00:13:59,290
it's inevitable to have injuries.

312
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:01,960
But the reason I insist on this

313
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:04,080
is that I learned it from you.

314
00:14:09,680 --> 00:14:11,250
I remember when I was very young,

315
00:14:11,250 --> 00:14:12,130
Dad was unemployed

316
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:14,170
and he took the only savings

317
00:14:14,250 --> 00:14:15,250
to go into business.

318
00:14:15,560 --> 00:14:17,720
That's why we have our good days now.

319
00:14:18,800 --> 00:14:20,720
Dad, you know what?

320
00:14:21,290 --> 00:14:23,440
Actually, you are my idol.

321
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:31,650
Back then,

322
00:14:32,290 --> 00:14:33,890
I was taking a gamble.

323
00:14:35,130 --> 00:14:37,440
It's different from your situation.

324
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:40,600
We have good living conditions now.

325
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:42,960
Mom and Dad will fully support you

326
00:14:43,170 --> 00:14:44,530
to study at a well-known school abroad.

327
00:14:44,920 --> 00:14:45,830
In this way

328
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:48,090
you will have a better future, right?

329
00:14:48,250 --> 00:14:49,440
I know all this.

330
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:51,290
And I also know many people

331
00:14:51,920 --> 00:14:53,800
advised you not to act impulsively.

332
00:14:55,080 --> 00:14:57,010
But you still made your own choice.

333
00:14:58,770 --> 00:15:01,080
I also don't want to disappoint my dreams

334
00:15:01,560 --> 00:15:02,560
and the people who love me.

335
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:04,800
So...

336
00:15:05,770 --> 00:15:07,650
So please let me be stubborn once.

337
00:16:20,900 --> 00:16:24,340
(Honorary Champion Wall)

338
00:16:24,340 --> 00:16:25,320
(Apartment)

339
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:26,650
- Lin Ge.
- Gao Kai.

340
00:16:28,050 --> 00:16:29,170
How is Nie Chi recovering?

341
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:31,040
A bit better.

342
00:16:31,130 --> 00:16:31,970
But not so quickly.

343
00:16:32,680 --> 00:16:33,520
Don't worry.

344
00:16:33,530 --> 00:16:35,400
As the saying goes,

345
00:16:35,650 --> 00:16:36,680
it needs a long time to recover.

346
00:16:36,770 --> 00:16:38,290
All right, thank you.

347
00:16:38,610 --> 00:16:39,450
I gotta go.

348
00:16:40,710 --> 00:16:41,580
Gao Kai,

349
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:43,680
I have a question to ask you.

350
00:16:45,410 --> 00:16:47,130
Many business people add me on WeChat.

351
00:16:47,770 --> 00:16:48,720
I am not experienced.

352
00:16:48,800 --> 00:16:50,250
I don't know how to refuse them.

353
00:16:50,650 --> 00:16:51,770
Aren't you short on money?

354
00:16:52,050 --> 00:16:52,920
Why refuse?

355
00:16:54,010 --> 00:16:56,290
This season is quite important to me.

356
00:16:56,560 --> 00:16:57,680
I can't be distracted anymore.

357
00:16:59,410 --> 00:17:00,290
Just be courteous.

358
00:17:00,920 --> 00:17:01,880
Give yourself some leeway.

359
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:03,410
Thank them first.

360
00:17:03,920 --> 00:17:05,490
Say you'll focus more on the competition

361
00:17:05,690 --> 00:17:07,200
and you may cooperate in the future.

362
00:17:07,520 --> 00:17:09,080
All right, thank you.

363
00:17:09,490 --> 00:17:10,330
Keep it up.

364
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:19,640
Lin Ge. Lin Ge.

365
00:17:20,010 --> 00:17:21,450
What's up? What happened to Nie Chi?

366
00:17:21,560 --> 00:17:22,400
It's not Nie Chi.

367
00:17:22,490 --> 00:17:25,250
Someone claims to be your town fellow

368
00:17:25,290 --> 00:17:26,840
and insists on seeing you.

369
00:17:26,970 --> 00:17:27,810
I don't know what's going on.

370
00:17:28,170 --> 00:17:29,310
My town fellow?

371
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:39,320
Are you looking for me?

372
00:17:39,600 --> 00:17:40,450
It's Lin Feng's sister, right?

373
00:17:40,730 --> 00:17:41,820
I'm Wu Jie, Lin Feng's friend.

374
00:17:41,830 --> 00:17:42,690
Do you still remember me?

375
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:45,840
When you just got home in your teens,

376
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:46,970
I stopped you with Lin Feng

377
00:17:47,080 --> 00:17:48,010
and you scratched my face.

378
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:50,140
You don't look like a good person.

379
00:17:50,800 --> 00:17:52,930
I don't remember. Get to the point.

380
00:17:53,050 --> 00:17:53,990
Lin Feng is hospitalized.

381
00:17:54,170 --> 00:17:55,250
He needs to undergo surgery now.

382
00:17:55,520 --> 00:17:56,560
But no one signs it right now.

383
00:17:56,920 --> 00:17:58,010
I really have no way.

384
00:17:58,150 --> 00:17:59,930
I remember he has a sister in Beijing.

385
00:18:00,110 --> 00:18:00,980
You are his sister.

386
00:18:00,980 --> 00:18:02,110
The hospital will allow you to sign.

387
00:18:02,280 --> 00:18:03,120
I'm not going.

388
00:18:03,140 --> 00:18:04,790
I have no relationship with that family.

389
00:18:05,010 --> 00:18:05,880
Ask his grandma to sign it.

390
00:18:06,970 --> 00:18:07,810
What are you doing?

391
00:18:08,530 --> 00:18:09,800
He is currently in the hospital.

392
00:18:10,020 --> 00:18:11,080
He needs to undergo surgery now.

393
00:18:11,080 --> 00:18:11,920
His family must sign it.

394
00:18:12,190 --> 00:18:13,760
How can I have time to find his grandma?

395
00:18:14,250 --> 00:18:16,010
Who knows if what you said is true?

396
00:18:16,120 --> 00:18:17,690
If you are really Lin Feng's friend,

397
00:18:17,690 --> 00:18:18,690
you should know

398
00:18:18,690 --> 00:18:20,050
how his family treated Lin Ge.

399
00:18:20,050 --> 00:18:20,930
How could you come here?

400
00:18:20,940 --> 00:18:22,600
- It's a matter of life and death.
- What are you doing?

401
00:18:22,770 --> 00:18:24,730
What are you doing?

402
00:18:25,450 --> 00:18:26,290
Who are you?

403
00:18:27,490 --> 00:18:28,330
What's going on, Lin Ge?

404
00:18:29,600 --> 00:18:32,490
Her brother is now in the hospital.

405
00:18:32,730 --> 00:18:34,290
He needs to undergo surgery and has no money.

406
00:18:35,120 --> 00:18:37,640
I really have no way.

407
00:18:37,840 --> 00:18:40,080
Her brother? What surgery?

408
00:18:40,360 --> 00:18:42,930
Lin Feng and I work at a construction site.

409
00:18:43,080 --> 00:18:44,320
Lin Feng fell from the scaffold

410
00:18:44,400 --> 00:18:45,450
and was pierced by a rebar.

411
00:18:45,930 --> 00:18:47,320
Just come with me to take a look.

412
00:18:47,560 --> 00:18:48,560
Just take a look.

413
00:18:50,210 --> 00:18:51,450
Is Lin Feng's family here?

414
00:18:51,640 --> 00:18:52,800
Lin Feng's family.

415
00:18:52,800 --> 00:18:54,800
- Doctor, this is his sister.
- Lin Feng's family?

416
00:18:55,270 --> 00:18:56,120
All right.

417
00:18:56,120 --> 00:18:58,050
Doctors from related departments

418
00:18:58,050 --> 00:18:59,150
conducted a consultation for him.

419
00:18:59,160 --> 00:19:00,160
Lin Feng's current situation

420
00:19:00,160 --> 00:19:01,170
definitely requires surgery

421
00:19:01,250 --> 00:19:02,930
to remove the steel bar.

422
00:19:02,930 --> 00:19:04,010
Do you agree with this plan?

423
00:19:05,210 --> 00:19:06,050
- Agree.
- All right.

424
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:07,560
Once the test results come out,

425
00:19:07,560 --> 00:19:08,550
the surgery can be performed.

426
00:19:08,770 --> 00:19:09,930
The doctor performing the surgery

427
00:19:09,930 --> 00:19:11,080
will talk to you again shortly.

428
00:19:11,160 --> 00:19:12,050
Do as you say, doctor.

429
00:19:12,050 --> 00:19:13,290
All right, then come with me.

430
00:19:13,290 --> 00:19:14,730
Let her stay here, ok?

431
00:19:14,730 --> 00:19:16,530
- Ok.
- Let's go.

432
00:19:17,930 --> 00:19:19,290
Call his grandma first

433
00:19:19,360 --> 00:19:20,840
and explain the situation to her.

434
00:19:21,360 --> 00:19:22,770
If she needs me to sign,

435
00:19:22,770 --> 00:19:23,610
then I will sign.

436
00:19:23,800 --> 00:19:25,250
In case something happens in the end,

437
00:19:25,290 --> 00:19:26,690
she will blame it on me.

438
00:19:26,930 --> 00:19:28,120
I've already made the calls,

439
00:19:28,210 --> 00:19:29,320
but his grandma didn't pick up.

440
00:19:29,320 --> 00:19:31,250
Call her as she said.

441
00:19:31,250 --> 00:19:32,320
Don't dilly-dally.

442
00:19:48,530 --> 00:19:49,370
Manager.

443
00:19:50,160 --> 00:19:51,000
Lin Ge.

444
00:19:51,050 --> 00:19:53,250
I talked to the doctor about his situation.

445
00:19:53,250 --> 00:19:54,090
The surgery cost,

446
00:19:54,250 --> 00:19:55,770
including the follow-up treatment costs,

447
00:19:56,350 --> 00:19:57,190
is not low.

448
00:19:58,160 --> 00:19:59,130
I've paid the money in advance.

449
00:19:59,690 --> 00:20:00,530
No.

450
00:20:00,600 --> 00:20:02,010
You said that the cost is not low.

451
00:20:02,770 --> 00:20:03,930
I have to find a way myself.

452
00:20:12,320 --> 00:20:13,730
Will you tell Nie Chi about this?

453
00:20:17,290 --> 00:20:18,560
Don't tell him for now.

454
00:20:19,600 --> 00:20:21,600
Don't tell the others when you get back.

455
00:20:22,640 --> 00:20:23,690
You can not tell others.

456
00:20:24,250 --> 00:20:25,290
Why don't you tell Nie Chi either?

457
00:20:27,600 --> 00:20:29,120
He's working hard on rehabilitation.

458
00:20:30,080 --> 00:20:31,360
He is already under a lot of pressure.

459
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:33,120
I can't help anything with him,

460
00:20:33,970 --> 00:20:35,290
I shouldn't add to his troubles.

461
00:20:38,290 --> 00:20:39,130
Fine.

462
00:20:44,800 --> 00:20:46,600
I've been busy with training these days

463
00:20:46,840 --> 00:20:48,600
and haven't had time to see you.

464
00:20:50,300 --> 00:20:52,700
(Lin Ge)

465
00:20:55,600 --> 00:20:56,440
It's ok.

466
00:20:57,040 --> 00:20:58,690
I have been recovering well these days.

467
00:20:59,290 --> 00:21:00,160
Focus on your training.

468
00:21:03,930 --> 00:21:05,120
I miss you very much.

469
00:21:08,970 --> 00:21:09,810
Me too.

470
00:21:19,010 --> 00:21:20,450
Don't be too anxious.

471
00:21:20,840 --> 00:21:22,320
Listen to the doctor.

472
00:21:23,500 --> 00:21:27,140
(Lin Ge)

473
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:29,730
Don't be anxious in your training.

474
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:32,450
If there's anything, remember to tell me.

475
00:21:40,490 --> 00:21:43,530
Ok. Good night and sweet dreams.

476
00:21:49,860 --> 00:21:52,020
Good night and sweet dreams.

477
00:22:04,740 --> 00:22:07,940
(National Ice Sports Base)

478
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:12,720
Lin Ge.

479
00:22:15,160 --> 00:22:17,930
Well, I need to tell you something.

480
00:22:19,930 --> 00:22:20,800
Your grandma

481
00:22:22,560 --> 00:22:23,490
has passed away.

482
00:22:26,320 --> 00:22:28,490
The neighborhood handled the funeral.

483
00:22:29,770 --> 00:22:32,320
I originally wanted my dad

484
00:22:32,640 --> 00:22:34,010
to go to her place to get the money

485
00:22:34,010 --> 00:22:35,010
for Lin Feng's surgery back.

486
00:22:35,360 --> 00:22:36,400
But in the end,

487
00:22:37,050 --> 00:22:39,010
my dad didn't receive a penny,

488
00:22:39,400 --> 00:22:41,320
but spent over 1,000 funeral expenses.

489
00:22:42,840 --> 00:22:44,160
That's Master's style.

490
00:22:46,250 --> 00:22:47,970
What do you plan to do next?

491
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:50,050
With Lin Feng's situation,

492
00:22:50,560 --> 00:22:51,930
even after the surgery is done,

493
00:22:52,050 --> 00:22:53,880
he won't recover in a short time.

494
00:22:54,160 --> 00:22:55,800
We can't earn much anyway.

495
00:22:56,970 --> 00:22:58,930
You have spent all of your money, huh?

496
00:23:00,530 --> 00:23:02,560
No worries. I still have some money...

497
00:23:02,560 --> 00:23:04,080
Don't worry about money.

498
00:23:04,450 --> 00:23:06,160
Don't tell your dad and mom either.

499
00:23:09,010 --> 00:23:10,320
I will think of a solution myself.

500
00:23:13,560 --> 00:23:15,450
Sorry, I'm late.

501
00:23:15,600 --> 00:23:17,050
It's ok. I just arrived too.

502
00:23:17,390 --> 00:23:18,250
Their food don't contain

503
00:23:18,250 --> 00:23:19,640
illegal additives.

504
00:23:19,700 --> 00:23:20,800
You should be able to eat it, right?

505
00:23:22,120 --> 00:23:23,250
I can try a little bit.

506
00:23:23,690 --> 00:23:25,120
Mainly because the calories are too high.

507
00:23:25,770 --> 00:23:27,800
About the live broadcast,

508
00:23:27,800 --> 00:23:28,930
how have you considered it?

509
00:23:28,930 --> 00:23:30,050
I'm really sorry.

510
00:23:30,320 --> 00:23:31,800
Our team is collaborating with a brand.

511
00:23:31,800 --> 00:23:33,080
It should be your competitor.

512
00:23:33,080 --> 00:23:34,290
I'm afraid I can't do it.

513
00:23:34,290 --> 00:23:35,970
Don't reject me so quickly.

514
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:39,080
We can't make it clear over WeChat,

515
00:23:39,120 --> 00:23:41,360
so I want to meet and talk.

516
00:23:41,490 --> 00:23:42,330
First of all,

517
00:23:42,490 --> 00:23:43,880
the part you are involved in

518
00:23:43,930 --> 00:23:46,160
doesn't involve brand promotion or sales.

519
00:23:46,290 --> 00:23:47,250
This is a co-branded

520
00:23:47,250 --> 00:23:48,640
charity activity that we are doing

521
00:23:48,690 --> 00:23:51,120
together with the chamber of commerce.

522
00:23:51,450 --> 00:23:52,290
We come to you

523
00:23:52,310 --> 00:23:53,840
because we hope you can

524
00:23:53,930 --> 00:23:55,560
support our products as a star.

525
00:23:55,690 --> 00:23:56,770
You just need to say a few words.

526
00:23:56,880 --> 00:23:57,720
Secondly,

527
00:23:58,290 --> 00:24:00,690
in terms of price, we are very sincere.

528
00:24:00,770 --> 00:24:01,730
You can take a look.

529
00:24:03,860 --> 00:24:06,010
(100,000 yuan)
We know about the competitor.

530
00:24:06,290 --> 00:24:08,120
But after the World Championship,

531
00:24:08,400 --> 00:24:10,800
your contract with them should be expired.

532
00:24:11,290 --> 00:24:12,640
The live broadcast

533
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:14,800
is before the World Championship, right?

534
00:24:15,050 --> 00:24:16,120
We say it is a live broadcast,

535
00:24:16,250 --> 00:24:17,690
but in fact, it is pre-recorded.

536
00:24:17,770 --> 00:24:19,360
We invite you to our company

537
00:24:19,400 --> 00:24:21,010
to shoot a video,

538
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:23,020
and we broadcast it when the time comes.

539
00:24:23,120 --> 00:24:25,380
See, there is a time on it.

540
00:24:25,380 --> 00:24:26,550
(Broadcast time)
It's stated clearly.

541
00:24:26,550 --> 00:24:28,690
It is after the World Championship, right?

542
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:30,480
Moreover,

543
00:24:30,530 --> 00:24:32,360
we have four or five candidates.

544
00:24:32,490 --> 00:24:34,210
But I come to you first.

545
00:24:34,400 --> 00:24:35,600
We have been in contact before.

546
00:24:35,690 --> 00:24:36,970
And I especially like you.

547
00:24:37,210 --> 00:24:39,050
I really want to give you this opportunity.

548
00:24:40,210 --> 00:24:41,120
Thank you.

549
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:42,360
Can I take this contract

550
00:24:42,360 --> 00:24:43,290
back to have a look at it?

551
00:24:43,290 --> 00:24:45,490
I'm willing to let you take it back.

552
00:24:45,730 --> 00:24:47,010
But my colleague

553
00:24:47,010 --> 00:24:48,320
is also in contact with others.

554
00:24:48,560 --> 00:24:50,450
If they sign it first,

555
00:24:51,180 --> 00:24:52,870
I might not be able to wait for you.

556
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:54,000
Well...

557
00:24:59,820 --> 00:25:03,010
I heard your brother is having surgery.

558
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:04,660
It must have cost a lot of money.

559
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:06,400
How do you know?

560
00:25:06,400 --> 00:25:07,770
I am the PR for the brand.

561
00:25:07,880 --> 00:25:08,970
I did some research.

562
00:25:09,400 --> 00:25:10,320
But you can rest assured.

563
00:25:10,530 --> 00:25:11,380
I would never tell others

564
00:25:11,380 --> 00:25:13,000
about this matter.

565
00:25:17,800 --> 00:25:18,640
Don't worry.

